parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the torque converter can cause the vehicle to shudder or hesitate when accelerating, which can lead to loss of control and accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden explosion of the sunroof can cause damage to the vehicle and potentially injure occupants.

often with a loud noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Musty or musky odors from the air conditioning system can cause discomfort and health issues for occupants.
symptoms: The air conditioning system emits a musty or musky odor.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunctioning audio systems can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The audio system fails to function properly
with issues such as loading errors
poor tuning
and insensitive touch screens.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Fuel system issues can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, leading to accidents or strandings.
symptoms: The vehicle emits a strong
unpleasant odor
especially when accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunctioning door locks can cause inconvenience and safety risks, especially if the doors fail to lock or unlock properly.
symptoms: The door locks fail to function properly
with issues such as remote lock/unlock failure and powered door lock failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical steering system can cause the power steering to malfunction, leading to a loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The steering wheel becomes hard to turn
the power steering light comes on
the steering wheel shakes violently
the vehicle wanders or drifts to one side
the airbag light comes on
and the radio and other electrical systems malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to a failure to deploy in the event of an accident, resulting in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag light comes on
the airbag system malfunctions
and the airbags fail to deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle stalling and acceleration issues can lead to a loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or accelerates unexpectedly
the vehicle wanders or drifts to one side
and the power steering light comes on.
